{"tid":608111,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"現實同夢想（入黎望一望講下你的睇法）","createTime":"2018-03-28T01:39:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-28T05:54:53.000Z","uid":132931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"988a01d44b9531178449b848d0f2ae782f73adcf","tid":608111,"uid":132931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T01:39:46.000Z","msg":"係香港咁現實的社會環境下，我諗大家普遍都係以錢行先。<br />\n大家都不得不放底曾經有的夢想，向現實低頭，選擇照顧屋企或者慢慢做樓奴接受有錢佬的奴役<br />\n<br />\n有人話過：睇一個人唔應該係睇佢成功哥一面，而係睇佢為左成功而放棄Ｄ咩<br />\n<br />\n我想知的到底係Ｄ咩令你放棄夢想，或者係Ｄ咩令你唔想向現實低頭？<br />\n背後個理由係Ｄ咩？甚至係因為選擇而放棄左Ｄ咩？<br />\n<br />\n當然我都知道有Ｄ巴打好勁，兩者兼備，但我都相信會遇到兩難的時候，你地又係點樣解決？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"023d9321fbf52c0235f0bfd2b6105938b3fcdf5d","tid":608111,"uid":132931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T01:48:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8d6f6dbeaf57c0597cff9d63c4243b219f4d101","tid":608111,"uid":132931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T01:59:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23dd06f1b19bffe46641d234492195b6695aaf56","tid":608111,"uid":125733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T02:02:01.000Z","msg":"believe in yourself"},{"pid":"b208492b3bb6040e783451f662f765132c7b0f5b","tid":608111,"uid":132931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23dd06f1b19bffe46641d234492195b6695aaf56","tid":608111,"uid":125733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T02:02:01.000Z","msg":"believe in yourself"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T02:15:52.000Z","msg":"講多D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9214308688f40ee28796f5707516ec9c0adb27c3","tid":608111,"uid":132931,"like":0,"disl